\fs30 \cf0 Sometimes it is not possible to access the \'93raw\'94 data (say, confidential genotypes in human genetics). In such a case, eqtlbma_bf can still computes the Bayes factors using summary statistics. Note that, for the moment, it only works with \'91--error uvlr\'92.
